Gloomy? Is it, really? My head kind of wanders whenever I read hero stories and lots of people really do not appreciate the hard job the hero does. 
You're the hero, so, you're just a tool we use to get rid of the demon king... really? How about I ditch you and then you can come and beg me to rescue you when the demon army comes? And you won't expect me to beat the demon king since once I do, you will clearly get rid of me...
So yeah, having the hero have his happy ending and the demons enact justice on that ungrateful bunch is fine for me.
